<HEAD>With AM-Cannes</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CANNES, France (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Winners of awards Tuesday night at the
42nd International Film Festival at Cannes:
   _ Golden Palm: ``sex, lies and videotape,'' United States,
directed by Steven Soderbergh.
   _ Special Jury Prize: (tie) ``Trop Belle Pour Toi'' (``Too
Beautiful for You''), French, directed by Bertrand Blier; ``Nuovo
